release.description:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at v0.4.1 -->

This point release is primarily for updating our nc dependency version , as the last update was breaking musl static builds, see https://github.com/containers/youki/issues/2894 . Apart from that there are not changes in this point release. You can skip updating if you do not use musl/ not experienced any breakage related to to builds.

## What's Changed
### 🧪 Test improvements and Misc Fixes
* update nc version to 0.9.3 by dependabot in https://github.com/containers/youki/pull/2895
* prepare for version 0.4.1 by @YJDoc2 in https://github.com/containers/youki/pull/2897
* Update Cargo.toml for v0.4.1 by @utam0k in https://github.com/containers/youki/pull/2904
### Other Changes
* Release for v0.4.1 by @github-actions in https://github.com/containers/youki/pull/2896


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/containers/youki/compare/v0.4.0...v0.4.1
